message:
Update on missing 14yo in New Jersey. Law enforcement working to bring her home. 
#Missing 
#NJ
#Philadelphia

data.description: Hannah Jones, 14, was absorbed into a human trafficking ring operating in South Philly, according to police. She is from New Jersey, and ran away a week ago. Officers and the FBI believed they were going to bring Hannah home safely, but the man she was with sped off, hitting a sheriff's deputy. Deven Harley, 32, was taken into custody, charged with aggravated assault. Hannah got away. I talked with Hannah's mom. That report will air on CBS Philly at 11:30 pm and #CWPhilly at 10. #HannahJones
